# Cleanup Whitelist
# Files and directories listed here are EXPLICITLY SAFE to clean when old
# Only files matching these patterns will be considered for cleanup
# One pattern per line, supports basic glob patterns

# ================================
# EXPLICITLY SAFE TO CLEAN
# ================================

# Price data files - regenerated automatically from yfinance
csv/price_data/*.csv

# Strategy equity curve files - generated during analysis runs
